OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784638108
OL,3,CPFAS report calls for clear legal
OL,4,Climits in water supply
OL,6,FAn independent report into the impact
OL,7,Fof 'forever chemicals' in Jersey says
OL,8,Fthe island must establish a specific
OL,9,Fand local definition for high PFAS
OL,10,Flevels in its drinking water.
OL,12,FWritten by the PFAS Scientific
OL,13,FAdvisory Panel, the fourth and final
OL,14,Freport on the matter focused on the
OL,15,Fimpact of the man-made chemicals on
OL,16,Fthe environment - including water,
OL,17,Ffood, soil, and waste.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784638108
OL,3,CPFAS report calls for clear legal
OL,4,Climits in water supply
OL,6,FIt advised that, in Jersey, levels
OL,7,Fabove 4 nanograms per litre in
OL,8,Fdrinking water should be considered
OL,9,Ftoo high, and trigger "immediate" and
OL,10,F"enforceable" action.
OL,12,FDescribing the definition currently
OL,13,Fused by the island as "problematic",
OL,14,Fthe report outlined how Jersey Water's
OL,15,Fuse of UK guidelines of 10 nanograms
OL,16,Fper litre is impractical because
OL,17,F"exceedances above this are described
OL,18,Fas common".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784638108
OL,3,CPFAS report calls for clear legal
OL,4,Climits in water supply
OL,6,FIt further explained these limits are
OL,7,Fvoluntary, rather than statutory -
OL,8,Fmeaning "exceedances do not trigger a
OL,9,Fdefined legal response".
OL,11,FThe experts added action should be
OL,12,Ftaken to treat mains water to achieve
OL,13,Fa level of 4 nanograms per litre
OL,14,Fwithin the next five years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784638108
OL,3,CPFAS report calls for clear legal
OL,4,Climits in water supply
OL,6,FThe previous States Assembly failed to
OL,7,Fmake a decision on these
OL,8,Frecommendations when they were made
OL,9,Fearlier this year - after Jersey Water
OL,10,Fargued the necessary technological
OL,11,Fupdates could cost up to #210 million,
OL,12,Fnecessitating water bill increases.
OL,14,FThe island's new Environment Minister,
OL,15,FSenator Mary Le Hegarat, will review
OL,16,Fthe report and publish a formal
OL,17,FGovernment response later this year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
