FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784638108
OL,3,CPFAS report calls for clear legal
OL,4,Climits in water supply
OL,6,FIn a statement, she said: "Ministers
OL,7,Fare arranging technical briefings to
OL,8,Fensure that we fully understand the
OL,9,FPanel's findings, the work already
OL,10,Fundertaken and the matters requiring
OL,11,Ffurther consideration.
OL,13,FThis will help inform a considered and
OL,14,Fevidence-based Government response."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
