FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784638108
OL,3,CPFAS report calls for clear legal
OL,4,Climits in water supply
OL,6,FThe full report gave 31 detailed
OL,7,Frecommendations about the
OL,8,Fenvironmental management of the
OL,9,Fchemicals - including on new water
OL,10,Ftreatment technologies, food
OL,11,Fproduction, bore hole management, and
OL,12,Fthe destruction of PFAS.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
